                "invention-title": [
                    "Smelting method and system for blowing hydrogen-rich gas in blast furnace",
                    "一种高炉喷吹富氢气体的冶炼方法及其系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of blast furnace low-carbon ironmaking, in particular to a smelting method and system for blowing hydrogen-rich gas in a blast furnace. The method comprises the following steps: obtaining and storing green ammonia; carrying out pretreatment on the green ammonia; wherein the liquid green ammonia with the first weight is heated and cracked to generate hydrogen and nitrogen, and then the hydrogen and the nitrogen are mixed with the remaining green ammonia to obtain hydrogen-rich gas; the hydrogen-rich gas is preheated, so that the hydrogen-rich gas has a first temperature; raw materials are smelted through the preheated hydrogen-rich gas; wherein the combustion temperature of the hydrogen-rich gas reaches the second temperature through heat compensation operation. According to the method, green ammonia is prepared by means of renewable energy for transportation and storage, and carbon emission in the ironmaking process is reduced. The direct reduction degree and fuel consumption in the blast furnace are reduced, and meanwhile, as engine power or power generation fuel, non-carbonization in the green ammonia transportation process is achieved, and electric energy needed by the blast furnace is provided."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本申请涉及高炉低碳炼铁技术领域，尤其涉及一种高炉喷吹富氢气体的冶炼方法及其系统。所述方法包括：获取绿氨并储运；对所述绿氨进行预处理；其中，将具有第一重量的液态的所述绿氨进行加热裂解，以产生氢气和氮气，后与剩余的所述绿氨进行混合，得到富氢气体；对所述富氢气体进行预热，以使所述富氢气体具有第一温度；通过预热后的所述富氢气体对原材料进行冶炼；其中，通过补偿热量操作以使所述富氢气体的燃烧温度达到第二温度。本申请内容借助可再生能源制备绿氨进行运输储存，减少炼铁过程中碳排放。不仅降低高炉内直接还原度及燃料消耗，同时作为发动机动力或发电燃料，实现绿氨运输过程无碳化及提供高炉所需电能。"
                }
            ]
